title: Top tier exchange listing to enable strategic capital investment
body:
UDT is a project with incredible potential which can attract institutional and corporate capital. This type of capital usually operates on regulated exchanges and with KYC. That is why it is necessary for UDT to establish itself in a regulated exchange authorized for the USA (from where it originated).
For this I propose that from governance a budget be enabled for payment for the list or in the case of being free, the proposal is to comply with all the legal / bureaucratic procedures for it.
Following the requirements established above, the proposed exchanges to be listed which have listed other projects supported by coinbase ventures are:
- Kraken
- Binance
choices: Try list on kraken or Binance
